        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Preload URL skill search results",
        "body": "Closes #2917.\n\nSummary:\n- preload URL-query skill search results for `/skills` and `/search` route renders\n- seed the client hooks from matching loader data before the normal client refresh\n- cover the reported bianmaxingkong slug searches in route and hook tests\n\nManual UI validation:\n- Ran ClawHub locally against the public read backend.\n- Verified `/skills?q=japanese-conversation-scorer` renders the bianmaxingkong skill result without the empty state.\n- Verified `/search?q=japanese-reading-grader` renders the bianmaxingkong skill result without the empty state.\n\nBrowser proof:\n```text\n[proof] /skills?q=japanese-conversation-scorer\ntitle_present=true\nauthor_present=true\nempty_state_present=false\nmatched_lines=[\"日语会话测试批改\",\"@bianmaxingkong\"]\n\n[proof] /search?q=japanese-reading-grader\ntitle_present=true\nauthor_present=true\nempty_state_present=false\nmatched_lines=[\"日语朗读作业批改模板\",\"@bianmaxingkong\"]\n```\n",
